Module com.um_project_golf
Package com.um_project_golf.Game.GameUtils

Class Consts

java.lang.Object
com.um_project_golf.Game.GameUtils.Consts
public class Consts extends Object
The consts class. This class is responsible for the constants of the game. All key settings are stored here. Made to be easily accessible and modifiable.
